snippet.title: Project Ferocious - Gameplay presentation - Future Games Show E3 2021
snippet.description:
Here's a brand new trailer for Project Ferocious. This is a survival shooter in which you will discover a lost prehistoric world full of deadly creatures under the control of hostile forces. Project Ferocious is targeting a 2023 release date and coming to PC, PlayStation and Xbox.
Wishlist Project Ferocious on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1645630/Project_Ferocious/
